decoworld.model.world.entities.inventory.containers

Class Container

  • java.lang.Object
    • decoworld.model.world.entities.inventory.containers.Container
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<ContainedItem>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Inventory

    public class Container
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<ContainedItem>
    An item container for world entities. The Inventory class extends this to implement the player inventory. Created by bjwood on 18/08/2014.

        public boolean setViewSize(com.badlogic.gdx.math.Vector2 newSize)
        Set the x and y dimensions of the view of the container. The number of grid elements of the new size must be the same as the size of the container.
        Parameters:
        newSize - the new size of the visible container.
        Returns:
        true if the new size fits the container. false otherwise. - P3TE
